entry.title: Azure-Samples/todo-python-mongo-aca
entry.summary: A complete ToDo application that includes everything you need to build, deploy, and monitor an Azure solution using React.js for the Web application, Python (FastAPI) for the API, Azure Cosmos DB API for MongoDB for storage, and Azure Monitor for monitoring and logging.
